title: The After Show Talks About Cigars That Could Have Been a Contender
itunes:title: The After Show Talks About Cigars That Could Have Been a Contender
description:
You know which cigars made it to Contenders of the Year. On The After Show, we talk about the ones that didn’t make it into the pack.

The Cigar Authority is a member of the United Podcast Network and is recorded live in front of a studio audience at Studio 21 Podcast Cafe upstairs at Two Guys Smoke Shop in Salem, NH and as always you can find many of the cigars we discuss at http://www.2GuysCigars.com/.
